As my birthday got closer, I used to beg

01:43:31.840 --> 01:43:35.365
and beg for that horse.

01:43:35.440 --> 01:43:38.489
And every time I begged, Ron
would slap me across the face.

01:43:40.080 --> 01:43:43.129
It would only make me
beg more the next day.

01:43:47.600 --> 01:43:49.090
One night he came into my room
and he said,

01:43:49.240 --> 01:43:51.846
if I could keep his visit a secret...

01:43:53.320 --> 01:43:56.205
and if he could do whatever he wanted,

01:43:56.280 --> 01:43:59.489
then he would buy me
a horse for my birthday.

01:44:02.960 --> 01:44:05.281
And this went on for about a week.

01:44:07.160 --> 01:44:12.041
And when my birthday rolled
around, there was no horse.

01:44:12.120 --> 01:44:14.325
So, that night, when he came into my room,

01:44:14.400 --> 01:44:18.566
I told him that I was going to go tell
my mother what he had been doing to me.

01:44:20.880 --> 01:44:25.886
And he promised me that
he'd kept his end of the deal...

01:44:28.960 --> 01:44:32.407
and that there would be a horse
waiting for me the next day.

01:45:01.600 --> 01:45:06.561
Happy birthday, Caroline.
Here's your horse.

01:45:32.320 --> 01:45:35.205
Why did you look in the elevator?

01:45:35.280 --> 01:45:38.363
I think you wanted me to, Caroline.

01:45:41.800 --> 01:45:43.723
Goodbye, Caroline.

01:45:46.640 --> 01:45:48.125
Well, don't just go.

01:45:48.200 --> 01:45:50.441
Say something to me.

01:45:53.360 --> 01:45:55.010
Be well.

01:45:56.920 --> 01:45:59.491
As well as you can be.

01:46:14.360 --> 01:46:17.045
The ugliness of who
I've been and who I am now

01:46:17.120 --> 01:46:21.444
is strongest when I get to see
my wife and children.

01:46:21.560 --> 01:46:24.285
I never told Lisa the truth,

01:46:24.360 --> 01:46:28.081
choosing instead to let her
imagine the worst of me.

01:46:28.160 --> 01:46:31.084
I think she decided that
whatever was in me now

01:46:31.160 --> 01:46:34.925
was dark and ugly
and better left where it was,

01:46:35.000 --> 01:46:38.209
as long as it was not near her
or the kids.

01:46:45.840 --> 01:46:47.885
What was I doing here?

01:46:47.960 --> 01:46:50.565
Maybe because it made me feel safer

01:46:50.640 --> 01:46:53.610
to know Caroline was far away from me,

01:46:54.920 --> 01:46:59.164
as if I alone were not responsible
for the wreckage to my marriage.

01:47:01.320 --> 01:47:05.611
Maybe to see her in a new life
would bring me some kind of closure.

01:47:07.720 --> 01:47:12.324
Maybe I'm just feeling stupidly
sentimental, like the asshole that I am.

01:47:22.600 --> 01:47:25.763
As the old reporter told me
on my first day,

01:47:25.840 --> 01:47:28.764
"It's all one story, kid.

01:47:31.200 --> 01:47:33.202
It's all one big story."

